This repository contains a technical assessment project created as part of a hiring process.

The project is provided solely for the following purposes:

* review by the potential employer or its authorized representatives;
* demonstration of the author's engineering skills;
* non-commercial educational and portfolio purposes.

This project is not intended to be used as a production-ready commercial product.

